// fetch-results.js
// GitHub Actions runs this ~20 min after each race
// Fetches: race result + driver standings + constructor standings from OpenF1
// Commentary: generated by Groq
// Output: races.json (single file with races, drivers, teams)
// ZERO human intervention required

